### Positive test: User can transfer money between his own accounts
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/accounts/transfer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic a2F0ZTE5OTg4OnZlcnlzVFJvbmdQYXNzd29yZDMzMyQ=

