### Positive test: User can change his name
PUT http://localhost:4111/api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic a2F0ZTE5OTg4OnZlcnlzVFJvbmdQYXNzd29yZDMzMyQ=

{
  "name": ""
}

### Negative test: User can't change his name with name with single word
